title: Titan Quest: Anniversary Edition (v1.48 + DLC) RePack by xatab
description:
At long last, Titan Quest continues its epic journey through the
world of antiquity. A mysterious threat calls the heroes of Hades to
the uncharted lands of northern Europe, where new enemies await and
new powers and treasures are waiting to be found! This new
expansion to the acclaimed Anniversary Edition of Titan Quest adds a
fifth act of unprecedented scope, along with many new and requested
features including new weapon types and a 10th Mastery for your
characters to learn
